@brody_thepuffer was hunting some ghost shrimps but my phone didn't record it 😭.

Despite the "ocean" song from the little mermaid, they are all freshwater 🤪

node.text:
Remember the day that Barry refused cockroaches and other insects?
It took me 2 weeks to get him liking insects, he even takes grasshoppers and crickets now 🙊.

Why did i do this?
To replace (seafood) mussels and prawn/shrimps because these are unhealthy for freshwater pufferfish due to thiaminase.
Insects are a healthy and nutritious part of the diet of freshwater pufferfish 🐡.
.
.
.
.
.
